  "description": "This individual is a broad-shouldered, middle-aged bartender with bronze skin and a compact, work-hardened build. Brown eyes sit beneath heavy lids, giving the face a steady, appraising cast typical of long hours spent watching a crowded bar. Brown hair is kept in a plain style, cut short to stay clear of the hands and the work. A flattened nose and thickened knuckles serve as lasting marks of a life accustomed to disorder at close range.",
